Changelog

fallRunDSM v1.0.0

fallRunDSM v1.0.0 is the Fall-run life cycle model used by the Science Integration Team as part of CVPIA Structured Decision Making process to evaluate priorities and information needs for management of anadromous fish in the Central Valley. A complete description of the model, model parameters and their source can be found in Peterson and Duarte (2020).

fallRunDSM v1.0.0 was run with the following data package releases to inform the Near-term Restoration Strategy FY2021-2025:

  • cvpiaTemperatue v2.0.1
  • cvpiaHabitat v1.1.1
  • cvpiaFlow v1.0.1
  • cvpiaCalibration v1.0.5
